            <h2>How are users moving through the site?</h2>
            <p>We can discover how each page contributes to conversion. Simple, measurable performance. What are the most valuable pages for conversion? Path analysis, decision trees, and probability theory are your new weapons. We will find which offers you could target at each individual client as he comes back to a certain page. Then plug any hole that leads people away from the desired action.
